<paragraph blockId="164.[189,1399,951,1083]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">
Species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Thuy, 2013" authorityName="Thuy" authorityYear="2013" box="[315,476,951,977]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiacanthidae" genus="Dermacantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[315,476,951,977]" italics="true" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">Dermacantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[482,587,952,978]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
with small LAPs; proximal to median ones devoid of vertical striation on outer surface; five small spine articulations; single moderately well-defined spur near outer ventroproximal and inner ventro-distal tips of LAP; ridge on inner side very narrow but with strongly widened dorsal tip.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
